  "prompt": "Who are some of the most beautiful Indian Women ever?",
  "response": "Beauty is highly subjective and can vary greatly from person to person. However, many Indian women have been renowned for their beauty both nationally and internationally. Some of the most commonly cited names include:\n\n1. **Aishwarya Rai Bachchan** - Known for winning the Miss World title in 1994 and her successful career in Bollywood and other international film industries.\n\n2. **Madhuri Dixit** - Celebrated for her incredible acting skills and dancing prowess, she has been a dominant figure in Indian cinema.\n\n3. **Priyanka Chopra Jonas** - Another former Miss World (2000), Priyanka has made a significant impact on Bollywood and Hollywood, as well as music and philanthropy.\n\n4. **Deepika Padukone** - Recognized for her versatility in acting and her stunning looks, Deepika has become one of the most popular actresses in Indian cinema.\n\n5. **Hema Malini** - Often referred to as the 'Dream Girl' of Bollywood, she has left a lasting impression with her beauty and talent.\n\n6. **Rekha** - Known for her unique charm and elegance, Rekha has been a timeless beauty in Bollywood.\n\n7. **Sridevi** - Often remembered for her doe-eyed beauty and exceptional acting, she was a prominent figure in Indian cinema.\n\n8. **Katrina Kaif** - Known for her striking features and successful career in Bollywood.\n\n9. **Sonam Kapoor** - Apart from her acting skills, Sonam is recognized for her fashion sense and stylish appearances.\n\n10. **Juhi Chawla** - Former Miss India and a beloved actress in the Indian film industry.\n\nThese women have left a significant mark not only for their physical beauty but also for their contributions to their respective fields, showcasing talent, charisma, and grace.",
